info.desc: This is what the intersection looks like when facing northward.
info.instr: Go to Nolte Center Garage. Make your way towards the west-most point.
There should be a door that leads to a short hall with stairs, go left.
Through a door this leads to an intersection (the first picture).
You will be coming from the center path, so you will navigate take a right.
After following this for a little bit, you will take a slight right
